{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "For all that they saw that the Jewish people went through, I figured-- because we were reading the papers-- you know, we didn't know that everybody, you know, was-- was-- almost everybody, you know, was, uh, gone, you know, to those selections, you know, and the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Everybody hoped, you know-- maybe somebody is left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And here those people that they saw what went on, they still say something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was unbelievable, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So I-- I started planning already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "No, I'm not going-- even before the war, you know, when I was a little boy, I was dreaming about leaving that haven in Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So here, I stand there and I said, well, this is time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then I heard-- I had-- I had a neighbor before the war, where we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he went through the war, the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So he said after the First World War, you could go every place, because the-- all the borders were open.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You didn't know no visas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You didn't need no visas, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I said, oh, I hope now is going to be [LAUGH] so-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But in the meantime, you know, you have to go through everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So we took us-- I think we'll stop this tape again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
